&lt;p&gt;You will define our solution positioning, build the value proposition and ROI narrative, arm our Commercial team with the tools to win, and turn customer outcomes into evidence the market believes. You&#39;ll partner closely with Product Management, Sales, Customer Success, and Executive Leadership — leading through influence to ensure that what we say in the market and what we deliver in the OR are one and the same.&lt;/p&gt;
