&lt;li&gt;You are a strong storyteller who can make a complex, multi-stakeholder solution feel obvious and urgent to a CFO, a perioperative director, and a value analysis committee alike.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You think commercially. You connect product capability to measurable business outcomes: cost avoided, revenue captured, hours returned to clinical teams.&lt;/li&gt;
